11#include "rtc_base/location.h"
12
13#include <stdio.h>
14
15namespace rtc {
16
17std::string Location::ToString() const {
18 char buf[256];
19 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%s@%s:%d", function_name_, file_name_,
20 line_number_);
21 return buf;
22}
23
24} // namespace rtc
